FROM (VALUES
  ('falling-start-to-5-10-yard-sprint', 'Falling start to 3–5 yards at 70–85% intent; coach at side.', 'No default sex-based adjustment. Scale by acceleration skill, power, body control, deceleration ability, and injury history rather than gender alone.'),
  ('two-point-start-to-5-10-yard-sprint', '3–5 yard start at submaximal speed; focus on first step.', 'No default sex-based adjustment. Scale by acceleration skill, power, body control, deceleration ability, and injury history rather than gender alone.'),
